	<description> Fix points to handle polar and radial chart stretching.</description>
	<discussion>
<p>
This method will fix a point to make sure it will layout correctly on a polar or radial chart.
The method can be used on a point regardless of chart type.
If no fixing is required then the passed in point will be returned.
Otherwise a new object or array will be created with the required fixes.
</p>
</discussion>
